:::Child replied to gigatron:::

Child: "The scroles's will rise now, it is the first of the seven steps to 
the begining of the human race.  In the next seven days many of the monkies 
and apes around the world will evolve, and on the seventh day they will look 
like they do in the year 2,000 AD."

:::As he spoke the hill infront of them blossomed into a gold and silver 
flower. in the center of the huge flower were seven lions with great golden 
wings. They lept off the flower and flew into seven difrent directions with a 
trail of golden light in there wake:::

Child: "They are the first, now for the second!"....
